Sale Pending
The seller has accepted an offer, and the property is now pending or under contract.

Delightful bungalow in ideal location near numerous shops, eateries, parks and BART. Enter into the formal living room with an attractive wood burning fireplace. Pass through to the open kitchen/dining room. This bright sunny kitchen has shaker style wood cabinets, tiled counter tops, stainless steel appliances and spanish Saltillo tile floors. The hallway leads to a full bathroom with vintage details including pedestal sink and hexagonal tile floors. Two bedrooms are at the end of the hall including a master bedroom suite. Pamper yourself in the luxurious master bathroom newly installed in 2015. A spacious shower with glass tiles, a skylight and a modern custom vanity. You will love it! In addition there's a loft space great for an office or guest room and interior access to the garage and laundry area. Mosey out back to a flat grassy back yard with a flagstone patio great for California outdoor dining. Perfect for play or relaxing.
